## Industries I work with

I have worked with small businesses across a range of sectors, but the principles are consistent: understand your customers, target the right keywords, fix the technical basics, and build authority over time. Industries I frequently support include:

- **Tradespeople** — plumbers, electricians, builders, roofers, landscapers
- **Local services** — cleaning companies, pest control, removal firms, locksmiths
- **Professional services** — accountants, solicitors, financial advisers, consultants
- **Hospitality** — restaurants, cafes, pubs, hotels, B&Bs
- **Retail** — independent shops, e-commerce stores, niche retailers

If your industry is not listed, that does not mean I cannot help. SEO fundamentals apply everywhere — the strategy just needs tailoring to your specific market.

## How we work together

The process is straightforward and designed to respect your time.

1. **Free consultation.** We have a call or exchange emails. I learn about your business, your goals, and your budget. You learn whether I am the right fit.
2. **Audit and strategy.** I audit your current online presence — website, Google Business Profile, competitors, keyword landscape — and put together a prioritised action plan.
3. **Execution.** I get to work on the highest-impact items first. You receive clear updates on progress and results.
4. **Review and adjust.** SEO is not static. Each month we review what is working, what is not, and adjust the plan accordingly.

There are no long-term contracts. I work on a rolling monthly basis or project basis, depending on what suits you best.

## Pricing

I offer small business SEO services starting from affordable monthly retainers, as well as one-off audits and strategy sessions for businesses that prefer to handle implementation in-house. Every engagement starts with a free consultation so I can understand your situation and recommend the right level of support.

For a detailed look at typical SEO costs and what influences pricing, see my guide on [how much does SEO cost](/services/how-much-does-seo-cost).

